%20tech%20a%20big%20part%20of%20his%20entertainment%20empire.%3Cp%3EParamount%20Skydance%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDavid%20Ellison%2C%20CEO%20of%20the%20new%20Paramount%20Skydance%2C%20wants%20Hollywood%20to%20stop%20fearing%20AI.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHollywood%20is%20divided%20on%20the%20tech%2C%20with%20some%20embracing%20it%20and%20others%20cautious%20of%20its%20impact.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EEllison%20described%20plans%20to%20use%20tech%20to%20consolidate%20streaming%20backends%20and%20improve%20content%20discovery.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20David%20Ellison%20takes%20over%20the%20newly%20formed%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparamount-skydance-david-ellison-deal-done-key-questions-answers-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParamount%20Skydance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20has%20a%20clear%20message%20for%20Hollywood%20grappling%20with%20AI's%20encroachment%3A%20don't%20fear%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20not%20going%20to%20be%20afraid%20of%20tech%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20embrace%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Ellison%20said%20at%20a%20press%20event%20Thursday%2C%20where%20he%20fielded%20questions%20on%20his%20plans%20for%20the%20newly%20formed%20company.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-investors-ai-hollywood-pitch-decks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20replacement%20for%20creativity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHollywood%20has%20a%20split%20personality%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI.%20Some%20like%20Lionsgate%20and%20AMC%20have%20publicly%20acknowledged%20recent%20deals%20with%20prominent%20AI%20company%20Runway%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-ted-sarandos-ai-filmmaking-cut-costs-not-kill-creativity-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENetflix%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shared%20how%20it's%20used%20AI%20in%20the%20content%20creation%20process.%20Others%2C%20like%20Disney%