rned%20about%20is%20all%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Sgt.%20Maj.%20Paul%20Hamako%2C%20pointing%20to%20the%20propellers%20on%20the%20drone%2C%20%26quot%3Bis%20going%20to%20get%2C%20you%20know%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20get%20in%20the%20woodline%2C%20and%20it's%20going%20to%20get%20hung%20up%20on%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20called%20it.%20When%20Aguigui%20was%20following%20his%20fellow%20soldiers%20through%20the%20forest%20of%20the%20training%20area%20later%2C%20that%20exact%20scenario%20occurred%3A%20his%20drone%20was%20caught%20in%20the%20thick%20vines%20of%20a%20shrub%2C%20and%20he%20had%20to%20quickly%20rip%20the%20vine%20apart%20to%20keep%20moving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hiccup%2C%20he%20suspected%2C%20is%20what%20led%20to%20one%20of%20the%20drone's%20cables%20malfunctioning%20later%20when%20he%20needed%20it%20to%20survey%20the%20area.%20%26quot%3BI%20wasn't%20even%20paying%20attention%20to%20the%20tree%2C%20kind%20of%20got%20tunnel%20vision%20and%20wanted%20to%20just%20follow%20the%20dude%20in%20front%20of%20me%20and%20ended%20up%20getting%20caught%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20explained%20that%20transporting%20the%20drone%20on%20the%20outside%20of%20the%20rucksack%20was%20something%20he%20hoped%20would%20work%2C%20but%20the%20drone%20being%20exposed%20to%20the%20environment%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20problem.%20What%20might%20be%20fine%20for%20an%20open%20field%20gets%20complicated%20in%20the%20woods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20Army%20drone%20operator%20wearing%20a%20headset.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68950c03194a2d49b8ae366e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20US%20Army%20drone%20operator%20wears%20a%20headset%20as%20he%20pilots%20a%20quadcopter.%3Cp%3EScreenshot%2FBusiness%20Insider%2FGraham%20Flanagan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EArmy%20drone%20operato