ic%20security%20interests%20and%20are%20making%20significant%20investments%20aligned%20with%20the%20President's%20America%20First%20agenda%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20an%20Intel%20spokesperson%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETan%20isn't%20the%20first%20leader%20Trump%20has%20criticized%2C%20but%20it%20is%20rare%20for%20the%20President%20to%20explicitly%20call%20for%20a%20CEO's%20resignation.%20He%20has%2C%20however%2C%20taken%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpaul-weiss-trump-executive-order-memo-law-crisis-workers-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheads%20of%20major%20US%20law%3C%2Fa%3E%20firms%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcolumbia-university-interim-president-resigns-after-deal-trump-funding-cut-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Euniversity%20presidents%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjerome-powell-trump-leadership-lessons-federal-reserve-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFederal%20Reserve%20chairman%20Jerome%20Powell%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20bring%20to%20heel%20institutions%20he%20believes%20don't%20align%20with%20his%20aims.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20remains%20fully%20committed%20to%20safeguarding%20our%20country's%20national%20and%20economic%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20White%20House%20official%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThis%20includes%20ensuring%20that%20iconic%20American%20companies%20in%20cutting-edge%20sectors%20are%20led%20by%20men%20and%20women%20who%20Americans%20can%20trust.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b145e040-837e-4d0f-bf16-ba5b3cb899b7%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDraw%20a%20line%20in%20the%20sand%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMichele%20Ehrhart%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20in%20crisis%20comms%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20and%20was%20VP%20of%20global%20communications%20at%20FedEx%2C%20told%