ted%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110242658ir-20%26h%3Dc9de173021f61b52083f2c0037fbe7850f04bc4db756906f26dba75ce1a8b00a%26postID%3D689102b845129e7dc8d43b3c%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fwindmill-air-conditioner-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwindmillair.com%252Fpages%252Ftaskrabbit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETaskRabbit%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20offer%20professional%20installation%20services.%20As%20someone%20who%20lives%20alone%20in%20a%20high-rise%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20never%20felt%20comfortable%20installing%20an%20air%20conditioner%20on%20my%20own.%20Most%20New%20York%20City%20buildings%20(including%20mine)%20require%20a%20metal%20bracket%20to%20enforce%20window%20ACs%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20turn%20to%20a%20professional%20for%20help.%20Still%2C%20I%20was%20shocked%20by%20how%20quickly%20he%20installed%20the%20air%20conditioner%20in%20my%20standard-size%2C%20top-open%20window.%20The%20installer%20took%20just%2010%20minutes%20to%20remove%20my%20old%20AC%20and%20fully%20install%20the%20Windmill%20in%20my%20window.%20He%20used%20a%20drill%20for%20the%20bracket%20and%20a%20pair%20of%20scissors%20to%20cut%20the%20panels%20to%20size.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20watching%20him%2C%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20say%20I%E2%80%99m%20confident%20that%20I%20could%20have%20done%20the%20installation%20on%20my%20own%20(maybe%20after%20a%20few%20reps%20at%20the%20gym%2C%20or%20with%20the%20help%20of%20my%20dad)%2C%20but%20I%20was%20surprised%20at%20how%20seamless%20the%20process%20was%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222e055665-3b28-4cc1-938f-79b3675ab237%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Performance%20%26amp%3B%20energy%20use%5C%22%3EPerformance%20and%20energy%20use%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20in%20a%20spacious%20New%20York%20City%20studio%20apartment%20(about%20500%20square%20feet%20total)%20with%20a%20bedroom%20%E2%80%9Cnook%E2%80%9D%20and%20a%20fully%20separate%20kitchen.%20I%20went%20with%20the%2012%2C000%20Btu%20model%2C%20Windmill%E2%80%99s%20largest%20AC%2C%20which%20is%20recommended%20for%20rooms%20up%20to%20550%20square%20feet%2C%20to%20cool%20my%20entire%20apartment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20this%20air%20conditioner%2C%20I%20had%20a%20different%2012%2C000%20Btu%20unit%2C%20but%20it%20was%20not%20sufficient%20to%20cool%20the%20different%20areas%20of%20my%20apartment.%20Previously%2C%20I%20could%20tell%20the%20outside%20temperature%20without%20checking%20my%20weather%20app%20because%20the%20apartment%20would%20heat%20up%20and%20down%20with%20the%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20tidy%2C%20well-organized%20room%20features%20a%20window-mounted%20Windmill%20air%20conditioner%20centered%20between%20two%20windows%20with%20closed%20white%20blinds.%20The%20unit%20is%20plugged%20in%20with%20its%20cord%20resting%20on%20top%20of%20a%20white%20radiator%20cover.%20To%20the%20left%2C%20an%20open%20closet%20system%20displays%20neatly%20hung%20clothes%20and%20drawers.%20To%20the%20right%2C%20floating%20shelves%20hold%20handbags%2C%20and%20a%20gold%20wire%20rack%20holds%20more%20bags%20and%20accessories.%20The%20space%20has%20a%20warm%20wood%20floor%20and%20white%20walls%2C%20giving%20it%20a%20bright%2C%20clean%20appearance.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6894f3ab194a2d49b8ae313c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Windmill%20AC%20is%20powerful%20for%20such%20a%20discreet%20machine.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Shinners%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20first%20use%2C%20the%20Windmill%20air%20conditioner%20has%20felt%20more%20like%20central%20air%2C%20reaching%20all%20the%20nooks%20of%20my%20studio.%20To%20truly%20put%20its%20cooling%20abilities%20to%20the%20test%2C%20I%20ran%20it%20on%20high%20on%20a%2093-degree%20day.%20It%20cooled%20off%20my%20apartment%20by%20about%206%20degrees%20in%20one%20hour%2C%20proving%20that%20it%20cools%20the%20space%20quickly%20as%20well%20as%20effectively.%20After%20one%20month%20with%20this%20air%20conditioner%2C%20I%20can%20confidently%20say%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20improved%20my%20overall%20quality%20of%20living.%20Plus%2C%20as%20a%20dog%20mom%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20noticed%20my%20pup%20feels%20more%20comfortable%20and%20energetic%20in%20our%20newly%20cooled%20apartment%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20affinity%20for%20this%20air%20conditioner%20has%20come%20at%20a%20cost%20(literally).%20Ahead%20of%20my%20last%20Con%20Edison%20bill%2C%20I%20received%20a%20notice%20that%20my%20energy%20use%20is%20projected%20to%20be%2034%25%20higher%20this%20billing%20period.%20Ultimately%2C%20I%20blame%20this%20more%20on%20the%20time%20of%20year%2C%20along%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20I%E2%80%99m%20actually%20using%20my%20air%20conditioner%20more.%20Windmill%E2%80%99s%20WisperTech%20technology%20is%20designed%20to%20increase%20energy%20efficiency%20with%20dual%20air%20flow%20and%20filtration.%20The%20brand%20advertises%20a%2015.0%20CEER%2C%20and%20in%20our%20at-home%20test%2C%20it%20registered%200.67%20kWh%20in%20one%20hour%20of%20use%2C%20which%20is%20average%20and%20%E2%80%94%20assuming%20average%20nationwide%20electricity%20rates%20%E2%80%94%20will%20cost%20about%20%2480%20a%20month%20to%20run.%20Of%20course%2C%20NYC%20electricity%20rates%20are%20significantly%20higher%20than%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20country%2C%20so%20your%20mileage%20may%20vary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22030298ea-9bf5-469a-b9da-29006075ff57%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Ease%20of%20use%20%26amp%3B%20noise%5C%22%3EEase%20of%20use%20and%20noise%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Windmill%20AC%20has%20been%20intuitive%20to%20use%20since%20I%20first%20turned%20it%20on.%20It%20comes%20with%20a%20remote%20and%20has%20a%20control%20panel%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20machine%20with%20an%20overall%20minimal%20look.%20The%20buttons%20do%20take%20some%20getting%20used%20to%20at%20first%20because%20you%20have%20to%20be%20up%20close%20to%20see%20their%20labels%2C%20but%20once%20I%20learned%20their%20placements%2C%20it%20got%20easier.%20You%20can%20toggle%20between%20fan%2C%20cool%2C%20or%20eco%20modes%20and%20adjust%20the%20fan%20speed%20using%20the%20buttons%2C%20remote%2C%20or%20app.%20The%20buttons%20and%20front%20screen%20light%20while%20you%E2%80%99re%20pressing%20them%2C%20but%20turn%20off%20after%2C%20which%20also%20keeps%20the%20machine%20discreet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20wearing%20a%20beige%20knit%20sweater%20is%20pressing%20a%20button%20on%20a%20white%20Windmill%20air%20conditioner%20installed%20in%20a%20window.%20The%20display%20on%20the%20unit%20shows%20%26quot%3B68%C2%B0%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BFan%26quot%3B%20mode.%20The%20sleek%20design%20features%20top%20air%20vents%20and%20a%20perforated%20front%20panel.%20A%20power%20cord%20is%20visible%20running%20down%20from%20the%20unit.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6894f2bb194a2d49b8ae30f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20control%20buttons%20are%20discreetly%20placed%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20panel%2C%20keeping%20the%20front%20face%20minimalist%20and%20clean-looking.%20%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Shinners%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20than%20anything%2C%20what%20originally%20drew%20me%20to%20the%20Windmill%20air%20conditioner%20is%20its%20promise%20to%20be%20quieter%20than%20other%20options.%20The%20window%20unit%20I%20previously%20had%20was%20so%20loud%2C%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20hear%20myself%20think%20while%20it%20was%20on.%20As%20a%20content%20creator%20who%20works%20from%20home%2C%20I%20had%20to%20turn%20it%20off%20for%20Zoom%20meetings%20and%20while%20recording%20videos%20because%20it%20was%20overpowering%20in%20the%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20turned%20the%20Windmill%20AC%20on%2C%20it%20brought%20an%20instant%20wave%20of%20relief%20along%20with%20its%20cool%20breeze.%20It%20gives%20off%20a%20low%20amount%20of%20white%20noise%20and%20sounds%20like%20a%20light%20hum.%20Using%20a%20decibel%20meter%2C%20I%20measured%20it%20as%2044.5%20decibels%20(dB)%20on%20low%20and%2055.4%20dB%20on%20high.%20It%E2%80%99s%20quiet%20and%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20any%20jarring%20noises%2C%20so%20I%E2%80%99m%20able%20to%20record%20videos%20and%20take%20audio%20calls%20without%20having%20to%20turn%20it%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20is%20that%20Windmill%20offers%20an%20original%20model%20at%206%2C000%20or%208%2C000%20Btu%20or%20a%20WisperTech%20model%20at%208%2C000%2C%2010%2C000%2C%20or%2012%2C000%20Btu.%20In%20previous%20testing%2C%20we%20found%20the%20original%20model%20to%20be%20on%20the%20louder%20side%2C%20at%2063%20dB%20on%20high%20(though%20the%20brand%20notes%20that%20it%20starts%20at%2049%20dB).%20If%20you%E2%80%99re%20looking%20for%20a%20quiet%20AC%2C%20I%20would%20definitely%20recommend%20opting%20for%20a%20WisperTech%20unit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243904878-e2ed-4cb9-82c7-a21694f59005%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Smart%20features%20%26amp%3B%20filtration%5C%22%3ESmart%20features%20and%20filtration%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20setup%2C%20I%20was%20prompted%20to%20download%20an%20app%20and%20register%20my%20air%20conditioner.%20The%20process%20was%20seamless%2C%20and%20personally%2C%20I%20appreciate%20a%20machine%20with%20smart%20technology.%20While%20I%20generally%20use%20the%20controls%20on%20the%20unit%20when%20I%E2%80%99m%20home%2C%20I%20like%20to%20use%20the%20app%20to%20turn%20my%20air%20conditioner%20on%20when%20I%E2%80%99m%20on%20my%20way%20home%20after%20being%20out%20and%20about.%20It%20has%20the%20same%20settings%20as%20the%20machine%20and%20remote%2C%20but%20is%20slightly%20more%20descriptive.%20Plus%2C%20the%20app%20allows%20you%20to%20set%20up%20automations%2C%20such%20as%20a%20schedule%20for%20the%20AC%20to%20turn%20on%20at%20certain%20times%20of%20day.%20There%20are%20also%20options%20I%E2%80%99ve%20never%20seen%20on%20an%20AC%20app%20before%2C%20like%20a%20setting%20that%20turns%20the%20AC%20on%20and%20off%20based%20on%20the%20position%20of%20the%20sun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20a%20white%20Windmill%20window%20air%20conditioner%2C%20with%20a%20person's%20hand%20lifting%20the%20front%20panel%20to%20reveal%20the%20internal%20filter%20and%20controls.%20The%20person%20is%20wearing%20a%20beige%20cable-knit%20sweater.%20The%20unit%20is%20installed%20in%20a%20window%2C%20with%20sunlight%20filtering%20through%2C%20and%20the%20power%20cord%20is%20visible%20below%2C%20resting%20on%20the%20window%20sill.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6894f450f748d8c055f717b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBoth%20the%20washable%20filter%20and%20optional%20carbon%20filters%20live%20behind%20the%20detachable%20front%20face%2C%20which%20can%20be%20swapped%20out%20for%20other%20colors%20and%20designs.%20%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Shinners%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20unique%20feature%20of%20the%20Windmill%20is%20that%20you%20can%20add%20a%20carbon%20filter%20for%20air%20purifying%20on%20top%20of%20cooling.%20(Note%2C%20this%20is%20in%20addition%20to%20a%20washable%20filter%20and%20isn%E2%80%99t%20vital%20for%20the%20AC%20to%20function%2C%20but%20the%20brand%20does%20recommend%20it.)%20You%20can%20purchase%202%20to%204%20filters%20from%20the%20brand%E2%80%99s%20website%20for%20%2425.22%20to%20%2445.24%20and%20set%20up%20a%20subscription%20for%20auto-renewal.%20Windmill%20recommends%20changing%20your%20activated%20carbon%20filter%20every%20three%20months%2C%20depending%20on%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b6c9cd51-bd3d-4e52-a8b9-0a9a484de3de%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3ECons%20to%20consider%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20set%20out%20to%20buy%20a%20new%20air%20conditioner%2C%20I%20faced%20one%20major%20hesitation%20with%20Windmill%3A%20the%20price.%20Depending%20on%20which%20Btu%20you%20choose%2C%20the%20units%20range%20from%20%24349%20to%20%24599%2C%20which%20is%20more%20expensive%20than%20other%20ACs%20I%E2%80%99ve%20personally%20purchased%2C%20though%20about%20average%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20picks%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-air-conditioner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20air%20conditioner%3C%2Fa%3E%20guide.%20However%2C%20now%20that%20I%E2%80%99ve%20experienced%20both%20a%20budget-friendly%20AC%20and%20this%20more%20expensive%20model%2C%20I%20can%20confidently%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%20worth%20the%20added%20cost.%20Overall%2C%20I%E2%80%99ve%20been%20extremely%20happy%20with%20this%20air%20conditioner%20and%20feel%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20improved%20my%20day-to-day%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20sure%20how%20I%20would%20feel%20about%20Windmill%E2%80%99s%20top%20vent%20since%20it%20only%20blows%20upward%2C%20and%20you%20can%E2%80%99t%20control%20the%20direction%20of%20airflow.%20However%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20actually%20been%20a%20benefit%20for%20me%20%E2%80%94%20I%20appreciate%20that%20this%20AC%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20too%20intense%20when%20I%E2%80%99m%20closer%20to%20it%2C%20and%20the%20cool%20air%20seems%20to%20disperse%20evenly%20through%20my%20studio%20apartment.%20While%20the%20AC%20has%20felt%20like%20central%20air%20to%20me%2C%20I%20could%20see%20how%20this%20could%20be%20frustrating%20to%20others%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20want%20to%20specifically%20target%20one%20area%20of%20your%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white%20Windmill%20air%20conditioner%20is%20installed%20in%20a%20window%2C%20viewed%20from%20above.%20The%20unit%20sits%20securely%20in%20the%20lower%20portion%20of%20the%20window%20frame%20with%20its%20vents%20facing%20upward.%20Through%20the%20window%2C%20the%20exterior%20portion%20of%20the%20AC%20unit%20is%20visible.%20The%20surrounding%20window%20area%20is%20clean%20and%20painted%20white%2C%20with%20a%20white%20power%20cord%20extending%20from%20the%20unit%20and%20resting%20along%20the%20windowsill.%20A%20portion%20of%20a%20radiator%20cover%20is%20visible%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20image.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6894f4c9f748d8c055f717da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20air%20blows%20from%20vents%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20unit%2C%20and%20there's%20no%20way%20to%20change%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20flow.%3Cp%3ERebecca%20Shinners%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFinally%2C%20I%20have%20run%20into%20a%20few%20minor%20annoyances%20while%20using%20this%20AC.%20First%2C%20the%20plug%20to%20this%20air%20conditioner%20is%20shorter%20than%20my%20old%20one%2C%20so%20I%20needed%20an%20extension%20cord%20to%20reach%20the%20closest%20outlet.%20Windmill%20ACs%20have%206.5-foot%20power%20cords%2C%20so%20I%20recommend%20measuring%20before%20installing%20them.%20And%20if%20you%20do%20need%20an%20extension%20cord%2C%20ensure%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20heavy-duty%20and%20the%20correct%20voltage.%20To%20be%20extra%20careful%2C%20I%20monitored%20my%20unit%20at%20first%20to%20ensure%20the%20cord%20didn%E2%80%99t%20heat%20up%20at%20all.%20Additionally%2C%20my%20AC%20has%20made%20a%20weird%20noise%20on%20a%20few%20occasions%2C%20which%20I%E2%80%99ve%20traced%20back%20to%20the%20front%20face%20coming%20loose.%20Luckily%2C%20this%20takes%20just%20seconds%20to%20fix%20by%20popping%20the%20cover%20back%20into%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c8c0ec1-796d-441e-b29b-3970bcca7a2a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%3