is%20growing%20and%20has%20seen%20opportunities%20to%20capitalize%20on%20the%20moment.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENATO%20ally%20Spain%20has%20decided%20against%20buying%20the%20US-designed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-mile-long-factory-where-f-35-stealth-fighters-made-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EF-35%20Lightning%20II%20Joint%20Strike%20Fighter%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20opting%20instead%20to%20invest%20in%20European-made%20aircraft%20for%20its%20air%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpain's%20decision%20comes%20after%20several%20NATO%20members%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrance-seizing-chance-trump-allies-question-f35-jet-europe-opportunity-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epublicly%20questioned%20their%20commitment%20to%20the%20jet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20made%20by%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20amid%20concerns%20about%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20attitude%20toward%20the%20alliance.%20Antagonism%20from%20the%20White%20House%20has%20rattled%20several%20American%20allies%2C%20though%20there%20were%20no%20firm%20decisions%20made%20concerning%20the%20F-35.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20makes%20those%20thoughts%20or%20ideas%20concrete%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mark%20Cancian%2C%20a%20retired%20Marine%20Corps%20colonel%20and%20senior%20advisor%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies.%20%26quot%3BHere's%20a%20country%20that%20really%20has%20changed%20its%20view%20about%20a%20future%20procurement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20Spain's%20decision%2C%20a%20Lockheed%20Martin%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BForeign%20military%20sales%20are%20government-to-government%20transactions%2C%20and%20this%20matter%20is%20best%20addressed%20by%20the%20US%20or%20Spanish%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Spanish%20defense%20ministry%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20the%20country%20was%20no%20longer%20considering%20the%20F-35%20for%20its%20new%20fighter%20jet%20acquisitions.%20The%20official%20did%20not%20give%20a%20reason%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.eu%2Farticle%2Fspain-scraps-plans-on-buying-f-35-fighter-jets-el-pais-reports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20Politico%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Spanish%20option%20involves%20the%20current%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnato-pilots-break-down-f-35-vs-eurofighter-training-dogfight-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EEurofighter%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20FCAS%20in%20the%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20directed%20Business%20Insider%20to%20the%20Spanish%20air%20force%2C%20which%20did%20not%20respond%20when%20reached%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20reported%20ministry%20statements%2C%20however%2C%20confirmed%20an%20earlier%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Felpais.com%2Fespana%2F2025-08-06%2Fel-gobierno-aparca-la-compra-de-cazas-f-35-estadounidenses-y-busca-alternativas-europeas.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0from%20Spain's%20El%20Pa%C3%ADs%20newspaper%2C%20citing%20government%20sources%20that%20said%20any%20plans%20to%20pursue%20the%20F-35%20had%20been%20shelved%20and%20preliminary%20contacts%20that%20had%20been%20started%20were%20suspended%20indefinitely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Aboulafia%2C%20an%20aviation%20expert%20and%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20US%20consulting%20firm%20AeroDynamic%20Advisory%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Spain's%20decision%20fits%20with%20%26quot%3Bthe%20broader%20European%20objective%20of%20sovereignty%20and%20self-sufficiency.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20under%20consideration%20is%20a%20fourth-generation%2C%20multi-role%20combat%20aircraft%20made%20by%20a%20consortium%20of%20European%20companies%3A%20Airbus%2C%20BAE%20Systems%2C%20and%20Leonardo.%20And%20the%20Future%20Combat%20Air%20System%20(FCAS)%20is%20an%20initiative%20from%20France%2C%20Germany%2C%20and%20Spain%20to%20create%20a%20sixth-generation%20jet%2C%20with%20an%20operational%20rollout%20planned%20for%202040.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAboulafia%20noted%20that%20Spain%20has%20a%20personal%20interest%2C%20including%20in%20job%20creation%2C%20with%20the%20FCAS.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpain%20has%20wavered%20on%20the%20F-35%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20sometimes%20leaning%20more%20toward%20other%20fighter%20types%20or%20extending%20the%20life%20of%20older%20aircraft.%20Its%20recent%20decision%20speaks%20to%20its%20new%20focus%20on%20European-made%20military%20technologies%20and%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20of%20anxiety%20among%20allies%2C%20including%20Madrid%2C%20over%20their%20relationship%20with%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f03de75-daec-4721-b8e7-2ec7d2718151%5C%22%3EA%20focus%20on%20European%20jets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpain's%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapnews.com%2Farticle%2Feurope-nato-defense-trump-war-russia-ukraine-b8d2097ab505e8e98ba08183bd181811%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20year%20that%2087%25%20of%20the%20more%20than%20%2412%20billion%20it%20was%20increasing%20its%20defense%20spending%20by%20would%20go%20to%20Spanish%20companies.%20El%20Pa%C3%ADs%20reported%20that%20this%20commitment%20was%20incompatible%20with%20any%20plans%20to%20buy%20fighter%20jets%20that%20were%20made%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225598%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22German%20Air%20Force%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20fighter%20jets%20fly%20in%20the%20sky%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6643cd44b4abc992e8c9848f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223732%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGerman%20Air%20Force%20Eurofighter%20Typhoon%20fighter%20jets%20fly%20during%20a%20media%20day.%3Cp%3EPiroschka%20van%20de%20Wouw%2FReuters%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInterest%20has%20been%20growing%20in%20building%20out%20Europe's%20defense%20industrial%20base%20and%20buying%20more%20homegrown%20gear.%20Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20European%20Commission%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrance-seizing-chance-trump-allies-question-f35-jet-europe-opportunity-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%20in%20March%2C%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%26quot%3BWe%20must%20buy%20more%26quot%3B%20European%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPart%20of%20this%20drive%20is%20Trump%2C%20whose%20rhetoric%20has%20created%20new%20tensions%20between%20the%20US%20and%20its%20longtime%20allies.%20He%20excluded%20European%20allies%20from%20peace%20talks%20over%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-did-russia-invade-ukraine-putin-politics-motive-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ERussia's%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20criticized%20the%20NATO%20alliance%2C%20and%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fheres-what-to-know-about-trumps-plan-for-greenland-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ethreatened%20to%20annex%20a%20European%20territory%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20also%20said%20last%20year%20that%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bencourage%26quot%3B%20Russia%20to%20attack%20any%20NATO%20member%20that%20doesn't%20spend%20enough%20on%20defense.%20And%20the%20tariffs%20have%20been%20another%20source%20of%20tension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20growing%20wariness%20among%20US%20allies%20and%20partners%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20weapons%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECanada's%20defense%20minister%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcanada-weighs-purchase-f-35-fighter-jets-amid-us-portugal-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%20that%20his%20country%20was%20reviewing%20its%20contract%20for%20F-35s%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20looking%20at%20%26quot%3Bother%20alternatives%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chairman%20of%20Denmark's%20parliamentary%20defense%20committee%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdenmark-f35-regret-choosing-defense-committee-chairman-tensions-us-greenland-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%20he%20regrets%20choosing%20the%20F-35%20for%20his%20country%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Portugal's%20defense%20minister%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fportugal-reconsider-f35-purchase-trump-us-lockheed-martin-ukraine-russia-2025-3%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPortugal%2520is%2520reconsidering%2520the%2520purchase%2Cmust%2520be%2520taken%2520into%2520account.%2522%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%20his%20country%20was%20unsure%20about%20plans%20to%20move%20to%20the%20F-35%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20pointing%20to%20uncertainties%20in%20US%20reliability%20as%20an%20ally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20politicians%20across%20all%20of%20Switzerland's%20political%20parties%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2025-08-07%2Fswiss-politicians-push-to-cancel-f-35-fighter-jet-deal-after-us-tariffs%3FleadSource%3Dreddit_wall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20that%20the%20country%20should%20withdraw%20or%20reconsider%20the%20planned%20purchase%20of%2036%20F-35As%20due%20to%20the%20tariffs%20Trump%20put%20on%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEuropean%20fighter%20jet%20makers%20have%20pounced%20at%20the%20opportunity%3A%20Eric%20Trappier%2C%20CEO%20of%20France's%20Dassault%20Aviation%2C%20which%20makes%20the%20Mirage%20and%20Rafale%20aircraft%2C%20said%20in%20March%20that%20the%20company%20was%20ready%20for%20countries%20concerned%20about%20the%20F-35%20to%20adopt%20its%20Rafale%20fighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225001%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20US%20Air%20Force%20F-35%20performs%20a%20practice%20show%20at%20Hill%20Air%20Force%20Base%20in%20Utah%20in%20February%202024.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680fcdfca466d2b74ab45d59%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223332%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20F-35%20is%20considered%20a%20top%20fighter%20jet%2C%20though%20the%20program%20has%20been%20plagued%20by%20various%20issues.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%20photo%20by%20Senior%20Airman%20Jack%20Rodgers%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20despite%20some%20of%20the%20remarks%20on%20the%20F-35%2C%20a%20widespread%20shift%20might%20not%20happen.%20Pivoting%20to%20a%20new%20type%20of%20aircraft%20would%20be%20a%20huge%20undertaking%20for%20countries%20that%20are%20already%20committed%2C%20and%20the%20F-35%20is%20considered%20a%20particularly%20good%20jet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAboulafia%20described%20the%20Eurofighter%20as%20%26quot%3Bequal%20or%20better%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20F-35%20as%20an%20air%20vehicle%2C%20but%20said%20the%20F-35%20%26quot%3Bhas%20the%20better%20mission%20equipment%20package%20by%20a%20wide%20margin.%26quot%3B%20The%20F-35%20is%20an%20advanced%20fifth-generation%20fighter%20aircraft.%20Furthermore%2C%20production%20levels%20may%20be%20a%20factor.%20Far%20fewer%20Eurofighters%20are%20made%20each%20year%2C%20and%20FCAS%20production%20has%20not%20yet%20begun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAboulafia%20said%20that%20he%20believes%20Europe%20could%20build%20enough%20fighter%20jets%20to%20cover%20the%20demand%20if%20it%20brought%20all%20its%20available%20models%2C%20from%20Gripens%20to%20Rafales%2C%20to%20the%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20limitations%2C%20though.%20Relying%20solely%20on%20European%20capabilities%20means%20that%20countries%20would%20have%20to%20make%20decisions%20and%20potential%20changes%20to%20their%20force%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpain's%20navy%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20an%20aircraft%20carrier%20that%20is%20currently%20equipped%20with%20an%20air%20wing%20of%20aging%20Harrier%20jump%20jets%20set%20to%20retire.%20The%20F-35B%20could%20serve%20in%20that%20role%2C%20but%20the%20Eurofighters%20and%20other%20European%20jets%20can't.%20So%20there%20would%20need%20to%20be%20a%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECancian%20said%20that%20he%20expects%20%26quot%3Bmore%20reliance%20on%20European%20suppliers%2C%20both%20because%20of%20concerns%20that%20the%20United%20States%20might%20not%20be%20reliable%20and%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Europeans%20are%20now%20investing%20a%20lot%20in%20their%20defense%20industrial%20base%2C%20so%20there's%20more%20to%20choose%20from%20and%20it's%20maybe%20more%20competitive%20%E2%80%94%20or%20will%20be%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20downside%2C%20however%2C%20is%20that%20if%20US%20allies%20don't%20pick%20the%20F-35%2C%20the%20interoperability%20with%20other%20countries%20will%20take%20a%20hit.%20%26quot%3BSince%20the%20F-35%20is%20used%20by%20so%20many%2C%20including%20the%20United%20States%2C%20that%20makes%20it%20easier%20for%20other%20countries%20to%20operate%20with%20countries%20that%20have%20the%20same%20equipment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20many%20NATO%20members%20are%20committed%20to%20the%20F-35%3A%20The%20defense%20ministries%20of%20the%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20Denmark%2C%20and%20the%20Netherlands%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-rattled-f-35-program-allies-arent-bailing-just-yet-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etold%20BI%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20they%20were%20unwavering%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Trump%20hardening%20his%20stance%20against%20Russia%20in%20recent%20weeks%20may%20dull%20some%20countries'%20worries%20about%20the%20relationship%2C%20Aboulafia%20speculated%2C%20but%20there%20continue%20to%20be%20rifts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpain%20is%20experiencing%20a%20very%20particular%20tension%20with%20the%20US.%20Spain%20is%20the%20lowest%20defense%20spender%20in%20NATO%20as%20a%20proportion%20of%20its%20GDP%2C%20at%201.28%25%20in%202024%20per%20NATO%20estimates.%20It%20al