0trauma.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CDeath%20may%20be%20comforting%2C%20but%20the%20courage%20lies%20in%20living%20and%20choosing%20life%20over%20anything%20else.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Manvi%20Mehta%20says%20these%20words%2C%20her%20voice%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20waver.%20It%20holds%20the%20weight%20of%20a%2016-year-long%20struggle%20with%20Bipolar%20Affective%20Disorder%20(BPAD)%2C%20yet%20it%20rings%20with%20a%20quiet%20strength.%20Today%2C%20at%2032%2C%20Manvi%20is%20a%20published%20poet%2C%20a%20professor%2C%20a%20mental%20health%20advocate%20%E2%80%94%20a%20woman%20who%20has%20walked%20through%20darkness%20and%20emerged%20bearing%20light%2C%20not%20just%20for%20herself%2C%20but%20for%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20journey%2C%20like%20many%2C%20began%20in%20silence%20and%20confusion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhen%20the%20brightest%20student%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20add%20two%20numbers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%205th%20September%20%E2%80%94%20ironically%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F364214%2Fteachers-day-radhakrishnan-abdul-kalam-jyotirao-savitribai-phule-history-pics-gopal-krishna-gokhale%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETeachers%E2%80%99%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20when%20Manvi%20first%20realised%20something%20was%20wrong.%20Then%20a%20top-performing%20student%20in%20Noida%2C%20she%20had%20just%20scored%2094%20percent%20in%20her%20board%20exams%2C%20topping%20in%20mathematics.%20But%20that%20morning%2C%20she%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20solve%20even%20a%20basic%20equation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-08-04T190519.721-1754314630.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Maanvi