3EDoctors%20initially%20suspected%20schizoaffective%20disorder.%20But%20after%20more%20tests%20and%20deeper%20observation%2C%20the%20final%20diagnosis%20emerged%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F234856%2Fsushant-singh-rajput-bipolar-disorder-misconceptions-care-giving-psychiatrist-india-nor41%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBipolar%20Affective%20Disorder%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20families%2C%20a%20diagnosis%20brings%20clarity.%20For%20Manvi%2C%20it%20brought%20rupture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20bipolar%20meant%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAll%20I%20knew%20was%20that%20it%20sounded%E2%80%A6%20final.%20Scary.%20Like%20something%20that%20would%20follow%20me%20forever.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Vishal%20Chhabra%2C%20Head%20of%20Mental%20Health%20at%20Fortis%20Hospital%20Shalimar%20Bagh%2C%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20someone%20hears%20they%20have%20BPAD%2C%20their%20sense%20of%20self%20cracks%20open.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20question%20your%20future%20%E2%80%94%20you%20question%20your%20past.%20Every%20mood%2C%20every%20decision%20starts%20to%20feel%20suspect.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBPAD%20isn%E2%80%99t%20just%20mood%20swings.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20chronic%20disorder%20marked%20by%20extreme%20shifts%20in%20mood%2C%20energy%2C%20and%20functioning%20%E2%80%94%20oscillating%20between%20depressive%20lows%20and%20manic%20highs.%20It%20began%20to%20reshape%20every%20part%20of%20Manvi%E2%80%99s%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%E2%80%99m%20depressed%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20sadness.%20It%E2%80%99s%20numbness.%20A%20fog.%20You%20lose%20all%20desire%20to%20live.%20You%20become%20hollow.%20And%20then%2C%20without%20warning%2C%20you%20swing%20to%20mania.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDMp