0it%20off%20instantly.%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20she%20was%20living%20with%20something%20so%20complex.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManvi%20kept%20her%20illness%20hidden%20for%20five%20years.%20But%20Kajal%20began%20noticing%20patterns%3A%20weeks%20of%20hyperactivity%20followed%20by%20complete%20withdrawal%20%E2%80%94%20missed%20calls%2C%20deleted%20social%20media%2C%20silence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20didn%E2%80%99t%20understand%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kajal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9Cbut%20I%20felt%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20Manvi%20opened%20up%2C%20terrified%20of%20losing%20her%20friend.%20Kajal%20didn%E2%80%99t%20flinch.%20She%20listened%20%E2%80%94%20and%20she%20stayed.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F480455%2Ffriendship-day-2025-then-and-now-landlines-whatsapp-video-calls-reels-real-stories%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETheir%20friendship%3C%2Fa%3E%20changed%20overnight.%20Kajal%20became%20Manvi%E2%80%99s%20safe%20harbour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20days%20she%20calls%20me%20crying%2C%20unable%20to%20breathe%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kajal%20says.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20I%20answer%2C%20always.%20I%20might%20be%20overwhelmed%20too%2C%20but%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20let%20her%20know.%20I%20help%20her%20ride%20out%20the%20storm.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ELiving%20with%20a%20mind%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20always%20obey%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManvi%20has%20been%20on%20medication%20for%2016%20years%20%E2%80%94%20mood%20stabilisers%2C%20antidepressants%2C%20anti-anxiety%20pills.%20Some%20days%2C%20she%20takes%2010%20just%20to%20feel%20like%20herself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20help%20me%20live%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20they%20come%20with%20a%20cost%20%E2%80%94%20weight%20gain%2C%20memory%20loss%2C%20insomnia.%20Still%2C%20without%20them%2C%20I%20fall%20apart.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20episodes%20haven%