%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20July%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98What%E2%80%99s%20your%20purpose%20in%20life%3F%E2%80%99%20Couple%20Gnana%20Saravanan%20and%20Krishnasudha%20were%20pondering%20over%20this%20quintessential%20question%20as%20they%20sipped%20their%20morning%20tea.%20Both%20IT%20professionals%20worked%20in%20the%20bustling%20city%20of%20Chennai%20in%20private%20companies%2C%20far%20from%20their%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%20is%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354716%2Fvegetable-farmer-smarika-chandrakar-grows-tomatoes-cucumbers-brinjals-in-chhattisgarh-farming-mba-grad-earns-crores%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeighth-generation%20farmer%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20first%20in%20his%20family%20to%20graduate%20from%20college.%20When%20he%20moved%20to%20Chennai%20for%20higher%20education%2C%20he%20missed%20the%20lush%20greenery%20of%20his%20family%20farm%20in%20Palakkad%2C%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20time%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20my%20purpose%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20to%20work%20for%20corporations.%20As%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20I%20felt%20a%20responsibility%20to%20give%20back%20to%20my%20roots%20and%20help%20sustain%20our%20generational%20farm.%20After%20all%2C%20it%20was%20the%20income%20from%20farming%20that%20provided%20for%20my%20education%20and%20that%20of%20my%20siblings%2C%E2%80%9D%20Saravanan%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKrishnasudha%20too%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20on%20a%20farm%2C%20always%20wished%20to%20retain%20the%20lush%20greenery%20that%20a%20farm%20life%20offered.%20This%20was%20a%20pact%20that%20they%20drew%20when%20they%20first%20met%20each%20other%20for%20marriage%2C%20she%20laughs.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20both%20wanted%20to%20return%20to%20the%20farm%20after%20working%20for%20a%20few%20years%20in%20corporate%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20thought%20in%20mind%2C%20the%20couple%20quit%20their%20jobs%20and%20returned%20to%20Palakkad%20in%202016.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20they%E2%80%99ve%20achieved%20and%20how%20they%E2%80%99ve%20transformed%20their%20farm%20since%20is%20an%20inspiring%20lesson%20for%20many.%20By%20leveraging%20technology%20for%20good%2C%20they%20mechanised%20the%20entire%20farming%20process%2C%20from%20creating%20natural%20fertilisers%20to%20setting%20up%20efficient%20irrigation%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20they%20developed%20value-added%20products%20like%20coconut%20oil%20and%20ghee%2C%20all%20produced%20at%20their%20farm%2C%20Deesan%20Farms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20model%20organic%20farm%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaravanan%E2%80%99s%20family%20owns%2036%20acres%20of%20land%20where%20they%20primarily%20grew%20coconuts.%20Although%20they%20practised%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352674%2Fgrow-bags-growing-vegetables-eyyo-kuriakose-kottayam-kerala-organic-farming-drip-irrigation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eorganic%20farming%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20input%20costs%20were%20very%20high.%20Upon%20returning%2C%20the%20first%20thing%20the%2039-year-old%20did%20was%20to%20implement%20integrated%20farming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Saravanan%20has%20made%20his%20farm%20self-sufficient%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2Fdeesan-2-1721657645-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-357935%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaravanan%20has%20made%20his%20farm%20self-sufficient%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20integrated%20farming%20system%20is%20a%20holistic%20approach%20to%20crop-livestock%20farming%20that%20combines%20agricultural%20production%2C%20animal%20management%2C%20and%20resource%20management.%20Its%20goal%20is%20to%20reduce%20external%20inputs%20and%20achieve%20self-sufficiency%20by%20using%20technology%20to%20recycle%20all%20wastes%20into%20fertilisers.%20Key%20components%20of%20this%20system%20include%20intercropping%2C%20advanced%20irrigation%20systems%2C%20and%20efficient%20recycling%20processes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20three%20major%20issues%20in%20farming%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESoil%20management%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWaste%20management%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EWater%20management%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20build%20an%20integrated%20farm%2C%20Saravanan%20first%20added%20a%20dairy%20farm%20with%2020%20cows.%20It%20is%20based%20on%20the%20output%20(dung)%20given%20by%20the%20cows%20that%20he%20designed%20the%20entire%20farm.%20The%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine%20are%20converted%20into%20natural%20fertilisers%2C%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3Epanchagavya%2C%20jeevamruth%2C%20amirtha%20karaisal%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20vermicompost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20answers%20we%20are%20looking%20for%20are%20present%20in%20traditional%20farming.%20I%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20efforts%20of%20my%20forefathers%20and%20father%20in%20building%20this%20farm%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20waste.%20Farmers%20have%20been%20practising%20soil%20conservation%20and%20balancing%20the%20ecosystem%20for%20ages.%20I%20use%20their%20knowledge%20with%20a%20small%20twist%20of%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20making%20the%20fertilisers%20manually%20is%20a%20time-consuming%20process%2C%20he%20installed%20a%20biodigester%2C%20which%20produces%20seven%20times%20the%20output%20that%20was%20being%20produced%20earlier.%20All%20the%20waste%20generated%20in%20the%20cow%20shed%20is%20sent%20to%20the%20fermentation%20chamber%2C%20generating%20almost%207%2C000%20litres%20of%20fertilisers%20daily%2C%20as%20per%20the%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5IhIfZSWFr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5IhIfZSWFr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5IhIfZSWFr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%