5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20how%20the%20Palange%20family%20funds%20their%20nursery%2C%20Trunali%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20mostly%20from%20our%20own%20incomes%2C%20and%20a%20few%20friends%20pitch%20in%20occasionally.%20We%20don%E2%80%99t%20really%20have%20any%20regular%20donors.%20But%20plants%20don%E2%80%99t%20need%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20to%20grow%20%E2%80%94%20just%20love%20and%20care.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20believes%20what%E2%80%99s%20discarded%20by%20one%20person%20can%20be%20a%20treasure%20for%20another.%20%E2%80%9CMilk%20packets%2C%20oil%20cans%2C%20jute%20bags%2C%20baskets%2C%20old%20pots%2C%20even%20plastic%20bottles%20%E2%80%94%20we%20use%20all%20of%20these%20to%20sow%20our%20seeds.%20We%20urge%20people%20to%20donate%20their%20waste%20to%20our%20nursery%20so%20we%20can%20use%20it%20to%20grow%20saplings%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FAarambh-Foundation_11zon-1754294155.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Vaishali%20Gaikwad%20from%20the%20Aarambh%20Foundation%20recalls%20her%20experience%20working%20with%20Bholewar.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20the%20sapling%20we%20planted%20stands%2015%20feet%20tall.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FAarambh-Foundation_11zon-1754294155.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FAarambh-Foundation_11zon-1754294155-300x139.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FAarambh-Foundation_11zon-1754294155-500x231.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FAarambh-Foundation_11zon-1754294155-768x355.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FAarambh-Foundation_11