C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T002646.452-1754295309.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20bawarchi%20(chef)%20cooking%20on%20a%20'chulha'%20(woodfire-stove)%20and%20sheer%20khurma%20being%20cooled%20in%20'mitti%20ka%20koondha'%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T002646.452-1754295309.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T002646.452-1754295309-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T002646.452-1754295309-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T002646.452-1754295309-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-31T002646.452-1754295309-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-480981%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cem%3EA%20bawarchi%20(chef)%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ecooking%20on%20a%20%E2%80%98chulha%E2%80%99%20(woodfire-stove)%20and%20sheer%20khurma%20being%20cooled%20in%20%E2%80%98mitti%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Eka%20koondha%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaqi%20mentions%20this%20with%20a%20shy%20grin%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20also%20people%20from%20Dubai%2C%20Pakistan%2C%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK%20who%20have%20reached%20out%20to%20me%2C%20telling%20me%20that%20their%20grandparents%20are%20from%20Lucknow%2C%20or%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F414598%2F10-places-to-eat-kashmiri-wazwan-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etechnique%20of%20storing%20%3Cem%3Esheer%20khurma%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20being%20cooled%20in%20a%20%3Cem%3Emitti%20ka%20koondha%3C%2Fem%3E%20(earthen%20pot)%20is%20something%20that%20has%20been%20passed%20down%20through%20generations.%20And%20this%20ability%20to%20connect%20and%20get%20that%20love%20is%20motivating.%20It%20feels%20right!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20that%20quickly%20went%20viral%2C%20Taqi%20portrayed%20the%20tradition%20of%20%3Cem%3Efalsa%3C%2Fem%3E%20sherbet%20as%20a%20beloved%20summer%20drink%20in%20Lucknow.%20He%20shared%20how%20the%20entire%20process%20%E2%80%94%20from%20selecting%20the%20ripest%20%3Cem%3Efalsa%3C%2Fem%3E%20berries%20to%20preparing%20the%20sherbet%20%E2%80%94%20remains%20a%20deeply%20cherished%20memory%20of%20his%20late%20grandfather%2C%20Anwar%20Nawab%20Sahab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20traditional%20style%20of%20storytelling%20struck%20a%20chord%20with%20viewers%2C%20many%20of%20whom%20flooded%20the%20comments%20with%20their%20own%20recollections.%20Some%20spoke%20of%20childhood%20summers%20spent%20sipping%20the%20tangy%20drink%2C%20while%20others%2C%20now%20living%20away%20from%20the%20city%2C%20expressed%20how%20deeply%20they%20missed%20its%20distinct%20flavour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20this%2C%20Taqi%20is%20certain%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20more%20than%20just%20videos%20for%20people%3B%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20reminder%20of%20home%2C%20heritage%2C%20and%20the%20loved%20ones%20who%20made%20those%20moments%20special.%20Perhaps%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20video%20resonated%20with%20so%20many.%20But%20he%20agrees%20that%20with%20all%20the%20love%20and%20admiration%20comes%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20breaking%20point%2C%20a%20limited%20team%2C%20but%20a%20strong%20will%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20is%20all%20of%20this%20really%20possible%20through%20the%20efforts%20of%20just%20one%20person%3F%20Taqi%20shares%20that%20having%20a%20strong%20team%20is%2